ğŸ”¢ Basic Calculator Web App
============================
This is a sleek and functional calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It performs all the essential arithmetic 
operations, and includes extra features like percentage, square root, and memory functions (M+, M-, MR, MC). 
Designed with a clean UI and smooth UX in mind!

